188
00:16:00,890 --> 00:16:03,200
<i>"Temptation of Wife" drama parodie</i>
Osoba, kterou jsi potkal, nebyl Go Mi Nam!

189
00:16:03,200 --> 00:16:03,600
<i>"Temptation of Wife" drama parodie</i>

190
00:16:03,600 --> 00:16:05,300
Jsem Go Mi Nam!
<i>"Temptation of Wife" drama parodie</i>

191
00:16:06,740 --> 00:16:08,130
Ty idiote!

192
00:16:09,070 --> 00:16:11,960
